data.description: Built in 2019 amidst the eclectic and artistic charm of Virgil Village, you will find this 3-bed, 3-bath gem. An industrial 3-level loft boasting a spacious 1526 sq feet has polished cement and hardwood floors, a floating staircase, stainless steel appliances, and the convenience of in-unit laundry. Soak in the sunset on the nearly 300 sq feet patio with stunning views of The Hills, Griffith Park Observatory, and the iconic Hollywood Sign. Escape the city buzz and unwind in the outdoor pool, fire up the BBQ, or break a sweat in the gym stocked with modern machines. This unit also includes 2 car parking spaces and a large storage unit. Just minutes away from fantastic Virgil Village eateries like Sqirl, Melody, Courage Bagel, and Budonoki Izakaya. Come make yourself at home in this inviting urban haven.
